name: .LMBAKE File Extension
summary: Learn about .LMBAKE files and view a list of programs that open them.

instructions: LMBAKE files are not meant to be opened or edited manually. If you want to view the data an LMBAKE file contains, you should open the corresponding .GODOT file in Godot Engine (cross-platform) and then edit the scene that uses your LMBAKE file.
